00:06:47.330 --> 00:06:49.890 align:middle line:84%
That's what "note" means
in the financial world.

00:06:49.890 --> 00:06:50.910 align:middle line:90%
It's a note.

00:06:50.910 --> 00:06:54.225 align:middle line:84%
I loan you some money, and
