00:06:59.900 --> 00:07:03.220 align:middle line:84%
And so a Federal
Reserve Note means

00:07:03.220 --> 00:07:07.640 align:middle line:84%
it's an IOU issued by
the Federal Reserve.

00:07:07.640 --> 00:07:09.530 align:middle line:84%
