00:07:15.460 --> 00:07:17.550 align:middle line:90%
It's a group of private banks.

00:07:17.550 --> 00:07:21.400 align:middle line:84%
So a Federal Reserve Note is a
piece of paper issued as an IOU

00:07:21.400 --> 00:07:23.740 align:middle line:90%
by the private banks.

00:07:23.740 --> 00:07:25.550 align:middle line:90%
That's what it is.

00:07:25.550 --> 00:07:29.050 align:middle line:10%
And will those private
banks ever pay it back?

00:07:29.050 --> 00:07:30.540 align:middle line:10%
