these people are?

00:08:36.190 --> 00:08:41.159 align:middle line:84%
And how have they tried to
build this cartel over time?

00:08:41.159 --> 00:08:44.260 align:middle line:84%
>>GRIFFIN: It's a very important
part of American history,

00:08:44.260 --> 00:08:47.240 align:middle line:84%
