surprised me to find out

00:08:47.240 --> 00:08:51.240 align:middle line:84%
that the Federal Reserve was
actually the fourth attempt

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:55.000 align:middle line:84%
to create what they call
a central bank in America.

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:58.030 align:middle line:84%
