called something else.

00:09:09.230 --> 00:09:13.250 align:middle line:84%
They're all central banks, which
means that they're basically

00:09:13.250 --> 00:09:17.290 align:middle line:84%
private banks in the
form of a cartel, which

00:09:17.290 --> 00:09:21.050 align:middle line:84%
have gone into partnership with
